item.title: XGN66-12-type-fixed-closed-switchgear
item.description: XGN66-12Z box-type fixed AC metal-enclosed switchgear referred to as switchgear, this product is suitable for power single busbars with a rated voltage of 3.6-12kv, three-phase AC 50hz, and a rated current of 630A-3150A. Double busbar and single busbar with bypass system are used for receiving and distributing electric energy.
